				An impressive guide indeed...I see you are truly an experienced wizard.I am currently level 20+,and I had a few more things to add,as some of the newer wizzy's may not understand certain tactics...they don't have to employ them until higher levels,and Id like to let them learn the easy way,rather than the hard way(Having big gnoll fists pound the truth into your thick skull)Personally,I don't particularly enjoy the sound of fists drumming my skull like a bongo drum,so,here goes.<BR>
When you get level 4,kill bunnies.(Green Creatures)Rats work well:) Root and shoot em to max out alter/evoke.Kill Gnoll Pups,and build up some cash...this takez awhile...they drop copperz regularly...so,you may want to trash decaying skeletons.Bone chips sell fer 1.3 silv...decent for that level...Now then,the biggest complaint Ive heard from newb wizzies is 'My root doesn't last 5 seconds!' The thing is...it shouldn't.Its a new spell.Your skill is terribly bad at this level.At level 16,I could root a gamble/tombstone for well over a minute...sow+root+Flame Shock(-110 DD)=dead gamble/tombstone...At level 18,I was camping Cordelia Minster solo...the faction drops are non-existant,and you GAIN faction with Mistmoore:) Those vampies LIKE you,if you kill her enough.Hehehe....amiable faction with Mistmoore,and Warmly faction with qeynos,indiff with Bards.Amiable with Ring of Scale...Stats on Cordelia...Lev 18-22 NPC...450-700hps...Low MR(root stuck throughout battle on gamble/tombstone once or twice)Med Fire resist(flame shock sometimes gets a nasty resist of 40-70%...occasionally 100% if shes a 22)If its badly resisted,sow will tell feet to take body to ride...Zone into west karana,and try again.I went from lev 17-20 in 5 days of camping her...several PP in coin,spell components,etc...enough to buy my spells.Advance through zones as such...<BR>
1-4-North Qeynos<BR>
4-8-Qeynos Hills,do Gnoll Fang quest at lev 8-12(Turn fangs gotten off Gnolls outside blackburrow entrance to guard captain in qeynos for MAJOR ep.)<BR>
8-12-Fangs til 12,12 group for Elite Ledge in blackburrow with a cleric...have cleric soothe one elite,and pull another,burn the one pulled,med ta full,and burn the other...spawn is now staggered,so they spawn one at a time,with enough time to med ta full inbetween)<BR>
12-16-North Karana...Kill Pincer Beetles til 16,then borer beetles til 17,then Scythes/Borers til 18...then Cordelia Minster til 20+<BR>
Contrary to what most think,our Melee skills stink...they'll always stink...and I don't even use a weapon anymore...Skull of Jhen'Tra,and Stein of Moggok...800+ mana and good group...Who needs a weapon?we can dish out over -1000 in no time.A good tank can taunt the thing inbetween nukes...Do NOT hold back your nukes...simply stand VERY far from the creature,and nuke away....if group forms a circle around the creature,its pathing ussually forces it to stay,as its path to you is (obstructed) by tanks.This is a trick Ive learned over the times...and it does work.Burn that sucker with Force Shock(Not badly resisted at 20,once skill is maxed...Mines resisted about as much as root...but,for -171+interrupt+knockback+2 sec stun,whadya want?Its a Magic Based nuke.)If the creature goes after you,root...tishans clash for -40+5 sec stun...and enough time for 1-2 -100+ burns.That should injure it enough for tanks to kill it while its distracted with trying to get around your skinspell(You aren't el-cheapo,are you?2gp for a 60 HP Invulnshield is great.)Thats all I can say,for now...tell you more as I advance.<BR>
<BR>
